T02D2718:84b-1: a'arya manydzu shr'i sto tra n'a ma /
T02D2718:84b-3: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi bstod pa zhes bya ba /
T02D2718:84b-4: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:84b-5: don zab sngags kyi stobs kyis rab sbyangs pa'i //
T02D2718:84b-6: stong gsal nam mkha' dri med dang mtshungs las //
T02D2718:84b-7: bam yig las grub dkar mdangs bdud rtsi'i mtsho //
T02D2718:84b-8: gting zab yangs pa can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:84b-9: mtsho mtha' glang chen thal kar gyis bskor zhing //
T02D2718:84b-10: mnyen lcug 'khril sdem pad zlum dra bas khyab //
T02D2718:84b-11: lo ma'i gur lding dkar mdzes me tog las //
T02D2718:84b-12: yid 'phrog dri bsung ldan la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:84b-13: mtsho chen dbus na bam yig las byung ba'i //
T02D2718:84b-14: pad sdong yal ga lo ma phun tshogs ser //
T02D2718:84b-15: 'dab rgyas dkar gsal ge sar dmar ser can //
T02D2718:84b-16: lte ba ljang ser mtho la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:84b-17: de steng yi ge mchog rab yongs gyur las //
T02D2718:84b-18: rab zlum 'khor lo rnam dag phun tshogs mdzes //
T02D2718:84b-19: shin tu mdog dkar yid 'ong 'dzin gzugs can //
T02D2718:84b-20: bsil zer phyogs bcur 'gyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:84b-21: der bzhugs aa dkar las grub dpa' bo'i sku //
T02D2718:84b-22: zung bzhi'i na tshod rdo rje skyil krung brtan //
T02D2718:84b-23: chu shel dri med ji bzhin rab dkar mdangs //
T02D2718:84b-24: mtshan mchog dpe byad 'bar la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:85a-0: thor tshugs rtse na rin chen @85a * //
T02D2718:85a-2: rtse mo lnga ldan zur phud shin tu gsal //
T02D2718:85a-3: snyan gong autpal dri ldan dar dpyangs 'phur //
T02D2718:85a-4: snyan shal nor bu 'phyang la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:85a-5: de bzhin mgul rgyan dpung rgyan phyag gdub pa dang //
T02D2718:85a-6: zhabs gdub ska rags do shal bzang ba dang //
T02D2718:85a-7: sna tshogs na bza' rin chen rgyan gyis spras //
T02D2718:85a-8: sil sil sgra snyan 'khrol la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:85a-9: phyag g-yas mchog sbyin legs par brkyang mdzad nas //
T02D2718:85a-10: g-yon pas autpal sdong po thugs kar 'dzin //
T02D2718:85a-11: srab 'jam dung mdog na bzas rab brgyan cing //
T02D2718:85a-12: mu med 'od zer 'phro la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:85a-13: dpa' mchog sku yi rnam pa dran gyur nas //
T02D2718:85a-14: rig sngags cung zad bzlas pa tsam gyis kyang //
T02D2718:85a-15: dus des dar dkar ma sha'i sbyor ba yis //
T02D2718:85a-16: phun tshogs blo gros spel la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:85a-17: gzhan yang gzhon nu dpa' bos legs bsten pa'i //
T02D2718:85a-18: ting 'dzin sngags dang ci rigs rdzas sbyor gyis //
T02D2718:85a-19: gnas skabs mthar thug yon tan ma lus kun //
T02D2718:85a-20: slu med nges par 'grub la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:85a-21: ngo bo ma nor chos nyid rab mkhyen cing //
T02D2718:85a-22: rnam pa ma lus chos can lhang nger gzigs //
T02D2718:85a-23: thugs rje che dang thabs tshul dpag med kyis //
T02D2718:85a-24: srid mtsho mtha' yas skyob la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2718:85a-25: 'jam dbyangs mgon khyod gus pas rjes dran cing //
T02D2718:85a-26: bsgom bzlas legs mchod mngon par bstod pa yis //
T02D2718:85a-27: blo ngan mun nag thibs po'i tshogs rnams kun //
T02D2718:85a-28: sprin med nyi shar ji bzhin dangs par mdzod //
T02D2718:85a-29: dpal ldan mkhas pa rnams kyi nang nas rgyal mtshan
T02D2718:85a-30: rtse mo ltar shin tu mtho zhing gsal bar gyur
T02D2718:85a-31: pa'i pandi ta chen po ma tis 'jam pa'i dbyangs
T02D2718:85a-32: kyi sgrub thabs dang bstun te /
T02D2718:85a-33: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i gsal 'debs bde ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi bstod pa rdzogs so /
T02D2718:85a-35: // / pa ndi ta sh'a kya shr'i bha dra dang //
